channel.title: Need help with setting up cache
channel.description: hello, im new too server making and i recently download a source,client and cache but i dont know how too set up the cache. Ive searched internet and youtube for two hours and havent found anything clear. PLEASE HELP

item.title: Need help with setting up cache
item.dc:creator: @Mikey96 Mikey96
item.description:
@Mikey96 wrote:

Hello, there is a file in your client called “signlink.java” open that and search for the “findcachedir” method, you can see where you need to move your cache to in order for your client to run smoothly. Message me if you have any further problems.
